ormacje przekazywane klientowi powinny w szczego&#769;lno</span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRoman; font-size: 12.000000pt">s&#769;</span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRoman; font-size: 12.000000pt">ci zawiera</span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRoman; font-size: 12.000000pt">c&#769;</span><span style="font-family: TimesNewRoman; font-size: 12.000000pt">: </span></font>
